&lt;li&gt;Undergraduate degree in Computer Science, Electrical Engineering, or similar quantitative field&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum of 3 years of experience in a business-oriented function&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong technical understanding and an ability to establish credibility with engineers and customers alike&lt;/li&gt;
